s, and for this reason he wanted tell the world about the plight of the Syrian people. This is  what he lived for, and died for. \nJames Foley is not going to be the advertisement of the book written by Mr Magdi Allam. Il Giornale must withdraw the advertisement immediately in order to respect the dignity of a dead person as well as the pain of his family.\n \nAvv. Luca Bauccio (Mrs. Diane Foley\u2019 lawyer). \n\nP.S. I would kindly ask you to share this press release everywhere, including on the social networks, so that everyone will know about this and so that everyone will be able to express their closeness to the family of James Foley and to their noble and just cause.", "source": "Facebook for Android (350685531728)", "link": "http://www.facebook.com/1556392945_10205206597635292", "subtype": "link", "received_at": 1414236662.0317, "media_type": "link", "type": "facebook", "id": "1e45c3a5c0a6a080e0665b749c8d3d06", "tags": ["tab7"], "schema": {"version": 3}}, "language": {"confidence": 93, "tag": "en", "tag_extended": "en"}, "links": {"code": [200], "title": ["Il COMUNICATO DELL'AVV. LUCA BAUCCIO,... - Radio Dirittozero | Facebook"], "url": ["https://www.facebook.com/DIRITTOZERO/posts/735404606526588"], "created_at": ["Sat, 25 Oct 2014 11:16:46 +0000"], "meta": {"lang": ["en"], "charset": ["CP1252"], "description": ["Il COMUNICATO DELL'AVV. LUCA BAUCCIO, difensore della Famiglia Foley, con il quale chiede a il Giornale il ritiro della indegna pubblicit\u00e0 del libro di..."]}, "normalized_url": ["https://facebook.com/DIRITTOZERO/posts/735404606526588"]}, "enrich": {"facebook": [{"username": "irene.righetto.75", "first_name": "Irene", "last_name": "Righetto", "name": "Irene Righetto", "locale": "it_IT", "gender": "female", "id": "1556392945"}]}, "demographic": {"gender": "female"}, "facebook": {"picture": "https://fbcdn-profile-a.akamaihd.net/hprofile-ak-xaf1/v/t1.0-1/c1.0.100.100/p100x100/317427_479826528751065_2067448380_n.png?oh=c6e1fadd3281143d7c18d453ab1aa1